        "items": [
          {
            "topic": "Personalisation",
            "topic_source": "dfa",
            "evidence_quotes": [
              {
                "quote": "targeted advertising"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "meta": {
          "skipped": false,
          "skip_reason": null,
          "validation_ok": true,
          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 9044,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "Digital advertising - and especially targeted advertising - is a lifeline for early-stage companies. It allows startups to reach their first customers, test market demand, and scale efficiently. Restricting these tools would disproportionately harm startups in smaller ecosystems like Bulgaria's, where access to capital and markets remains limited.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s0",
          "section_path": [],
          "span": null,
          "chunk_quality": "ok",
          "chunk_word_count": 46,
          "char_len": 349
        }
      },
      {
        "para_id": "p20",
        "items": [
          {
            "topic": "Personalisation",
            "topic_source": "dfa",
            "evidence_quotes": [
              {
                "quote": "targeted ads attract 162% more new and returning customers"
              },
              {
                "quote": "personalised advertising"
              }
            ]
          }
        ],
        "meta": {
          "skipped": false,
          "skip_reason": null,
          "validation_ok": true,
          "errors": [],
          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 14652,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "A 2024 Danish Entrepreneurs report found that targeted ads attract 162% more new and returning customers and reduce acquisition costs by over 100% compared to contextual ads. Moreover, 86% of EU SMEs report revenue growth through personalised advertising. These are not abstract statistics - they reflect the lived reality of hundreds of Bulgarian startups that rely on such tools to compete regionally and internationally.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s0",
          "section_path": [],
          "span": null,
          "chunk_quality": "ok",
          "chunk_word_count": 63,
          "char_len": 423
        }
      },
      {
