          "repaired": false,
          "latency_ms": 6243,
          "unit_kind": "paragraph"
        },
        "text": "Bulgaria's growing tech sector, part of a wider Central and Eastern European innovation hub, is a clear example of how digital entrepreneurship drives regional development and social mobility. The DFA should therefore be designed to empower rather than constrain such ecosystems.",
        "chunk_meta": {
          "section_id": "s2",
          "section_path": [
            "Strengthening Europe's Innovation Ecosystem"
          ],
          "span": null,
          "chunk_quality": "ok",
